1
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,800
Before Father passed, he left instructions.

2
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,240
Should he meet with calamity,

3
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,960
his soul rests in the lotus pond,

4
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,120
and Dharma echoes in his dreams.

5
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,720
Serving the light,

6
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,480
praying for the common people.

7
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,640
All appearances of mortals

8
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,960
are but illusions.

9
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,800
If one sees

10
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,920
that all forms are not forms,

11
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,560
then

12
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,600
one sees the Tathagata.

13
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,240
Master of the Tang Clan,

14
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:25,160
to ascend to the Pure Land before me

15
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,680
is a joyous occasion.

16
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,800
Master, your tone is open-minded,

17
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,360
yet why do you wear a look of tearless grief?

18
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,680
Disciple,

19
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:48,840
you have understood life and death.

20
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,440
Master,

21
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:05,440
how many days have you been fasting?

22
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,560
More than a month.

23
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:11,120
With the first realization,

24
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,880
one wakes as if from a dream.

25
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,440
With the second realization,

26
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,400
heaven and earth are filled with light.

27
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,120
Now,

28
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:21,400
my karmic entanglements are resolved.

29
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,440
I presume

30
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,280
the perfection of virtues is near.

31
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,280
Regarding life and death,

32
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,480
compared to us ordinary mortals,

33
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,280
you are far more enlightened.

34
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,600
I have heard

35
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:41,000
that you wrote a book with your life's insights,

36
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,280
titled "Dream of Divine Secrets".

37
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:46,440
Copied and revised dozens of times.

38
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,520
The book also contains

39
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,600
"speak not of divine secrets"

40
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,560
and techniques to defy destiny.

41
00:03:58,880 --> 00:03:59,520
Come.

42
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:04,920
You actually believe such absurd nonsense?

43
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:12,120
An old tree fears becoming hollow;

44
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,760
an old man fears becoming slack.

45
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,720
You...

46
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:18,680
not for a single moment

47
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:20,640
do you ever relax.

48
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,480
Very well.

49
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:24,680
I did compile a book

50
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,440
called "Dream of Divine Secrets".

51
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,560
However,

52
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:31,720
it is merely a chess manual.

53
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,760
My every move and step,

54
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:41,000
have you not yet fully grasped?

55
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:47,800
Good.

56
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:53,480
Then I shall strike first

57
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,520
and make the opening move.

58
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,640
That lacks wisdom.

59
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,280
Linggu Temple

60
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,640
It is still the same old place, as expected

61
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:18,160
But with some unexpected door gods

62
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,280
Today

63
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,960
I must trouble Director Wang and Lady Hua

64
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,240
to accompany me on this trip

65
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,160
It matters not

66
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:28,760
Today Lady Hua wishes to burn incense to Buddha

67
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,800
I am merely here to keep her company

68
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:38,200
It is Miss Hua Shuoyue of Blossom Pavilion

69
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,360
Her gorgeous attire and beauty are breathtaking

70
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,640
Yet she has the entangling beauty of a dew-laden flower

71
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,000
People say

72
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,760
she is a snake demon made of water

73
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,360
Born as a man

74
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:51,480
if one does not taste such flavors

75
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,360
one has lived in vain

76
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,440
Zhang Shaoqing

77
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,920
Poisonous snakes can take a man's life

78
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,840
That is where you do not understand

79
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,680
Grand Court of Justice Vice Minister Zhang Yi

80
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:03,520
pays respects to Director Wang, Lady Hua

81
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,520
Embroidered Uniform Guard Commander Shen Youzhi

82
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,680
pays respects to Director Wang

83
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,720
Lady Hua

84
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,560
Youzhi has become distant with us

85
00:06:13,280 --> 00:06:15,040
Learning the empty formalities of officialdom

86
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,920
In the past, you used to call me Sister Hua

87
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,680
Come, let me take a look

88
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:20,600
at your appearance now

89
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,720
What a dashing, handsome young master

90
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,960
It makes me somewhat regret

91
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,320
not teaching you personally

92
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,920
Has Director Shang arranged a marriage for you?

93
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,720
Three years ago, she and I both called him Father

94
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,280
We were close like siblings

95
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:36,600
Now she calls Father "Director"

96
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,400
There must be complications in between

97
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,000
It is better not to get too close

98
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:43,240
Father and I are in no rush to settle a marriage

99
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:44,720
Lady Hua

100
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,360
please do not tease me

101
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,600
He is just like this

102
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,960
a stiff and boring character

103
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,040
How could he understand

104
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,840
the teasing of this understanding flower?

105
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,200
Otherwise

106
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,960
he would not be here early in the morning

107
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:01,360
guarding the foot of the temple mountain

108
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,720
Could it be that at Director Shang's place

109
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,760
you suffered some grievance

110
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,520
and wish to accompany the green lamp and ancient Buddha?

111
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,320
It seems to be a twist of nine turns and eighteen bends

112
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,600
That is not the case

113
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,480
I am

114
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,160
Lady Hua has misunderstood

115
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:14,960
We are here to pursue the suspect

116
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,240
and track the whereabouts of Tang Xi and the others

117
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,120
We did not expect

118
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,040
to run into you lords

119
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,200
on your auspicious day of worship

120
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,720
It can be considered a coincidence

121
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:25,280
The enthusiastic Zhang Shaoqing

122
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,560
has actually reminded me

123
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:28,280
The time for the city lockdown is approaching

124
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,600
Closing the case is imminent

125
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,960
You must make the best use of time

126
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,640
to find clues about Li Chenyang

127
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,880
It is best not to let the Eastern Depot lose too much face

128
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,320
so as to avoid

129
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,080
hurting the harmony between everyone

130
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,240
Since you want to put on an act

131
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,280
yet you do not even fully decorate the facade

132
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,360
I fear there is something Director Wang does not know

133
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:48,520
Yesterday

134
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:51,120
the Eastern Depot and Grand Court of Justice were criticized

135
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,760
Lu Shijie behind you

136
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,560
Advocate Lu

137
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,480
deserves much of the credit

138
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,120
Lord Shen

139
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,080
you speak too heavily

140
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,280
What I said at the Grand Court of Justice

141
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:06,600
was all argued based on facts and the Great Ming Code

142
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:08,840
This is the difference between the Eastern Depot

143
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,840
and the Western Depot

144
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,680
You only remember the humiliation

145
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,120
Advocate Lu brought upon you

146
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,280
but never thought

147
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:18,760
to use his talent for yourselves

148
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:22,480
No wonder the Eastern Depot hoards

149
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:25,160
only those self-righteous

150
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,400
old deadwood

151
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,760
It seems

152
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:33,640
I misunderstood the Director's good intentions

153
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,680
You just can't stand seeing me by Father's side

154
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,680
That "Director"...

155
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,520
sounds like he's whining to you.

156
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:53,320
Don't bully Youzhi too hard.

157
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,880
If Director Shang gets annoyed,

158
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,200
you'll be the one whose heart aches

159
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,520
for his health.

160
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,440
We are brothers.

161
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,240
How can you call it bullying?

162
00:09:03,760 --> 00:09:06,120
Clearly, you are favoring this little brother.

163
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,080
However,

164
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,760
his current attitude towards us,

165
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,720
that familiar, reckless spirit,

166
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,840
actually reminds me

167
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:15,160
of some events from the past.

168
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,400
Isn't that so?

169
00:09:17,680 --> 00:09:18,960
He's just like you were in the past.

170
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,880
Since you have business to attend to,

171
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,480
I, this unserious person,

172
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:24,720
won't cause trouble for you lords.

173
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:26,320
Today,

174
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,000
Lady Hua comes first.

175
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,480
Let's go.

176
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:50,040
Thanks for your help just now, warm-hearted Zhang Shaoqing.

177
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,560
You misunderstand.

178
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,520
I just wanted to exchange

179
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,560
a few more words with Lady Hua.

180
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,120
As for you,

181
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,200
you have no respect for the Grand Court of Justice.

182
00:10:01,280 --> 00:10:03,360
It's a fact the Grand Court has no say here.

183
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:05,160
It's not intentional.

184
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,320
You'd better calm down

185
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:11,000
and continue being the warm-hearted Zhang Shaoqing.

186
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:11,920
Oh, come on.

187
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,640
Indeed, listening to the morning bells and evening drums

188
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,840
and chanting scriptures at the temple,

189
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,200
the distracting thoughts in your mind

190
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,320
have cleared up quite a bit.

191
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,840
If you stayed at Linggu Temple to become a monk

192
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,440
and seek a pure land in your heart,

193
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,520
I would certainly think more highly of you.

194
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:32,640
I was born a vulgar person.

195
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:34,760
I never asked for your high regard.

196
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,040
Lu Shijie.

197
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,120
You saw it just now.

198
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,640
Zhang Yi, Shen Youzhi,

199
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:42,520
and that old thing in the backyard

200
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,360
are biting down hard and won't let go.

201
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:45,440
Rest assured, Director Wang.

202
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:46,240
Last night,

203
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,760
we analyzed the layout map

204
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:48,560
of the temple courtyard and found that,

205
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,960
aside from the Pilgrim Hall's main entrance,

206
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,760
to enter the Linggu Temple pagoda,

207
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,320
one can only pass through...

208
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,520
The bamboo forest northwest of the Linggu Temple pagoda.

209
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,960
A view of fresh emerald green,

210
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:58,560
shifting and soul-stealing.

211
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,240
The Black Wind Formation.

212
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:01,040
Past mists punish the heart and seize the soul,

213
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,120
killing without a trace.

214
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:04,120
Do not covet viewing the world with your eyes;

215
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,680
listen for the formation's eye, the gate of life.

216
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:07,440
The deep swamp northeast of the pagoda.

217
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,920
Dense canopy blocking the light,

218
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,120
shifting Earth Fiends,

219
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,720
the Array of Diabolic Ghosts.

220
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:11,920
In the chaotic darkness,

221
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,440
one sees the likes and dislikes in one's heart.

222
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,240
Love, hate, greed, and desire—

223
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:16,400
to hold or let go, a single thought is the gate of life.

224
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,360
The courtyard due north of the pagoda.

225
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,560
Shifting Ambush from Ten Sides.

226
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,400
The eye holds the Eastern Depot's top shadow guard,

227
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:22,000
Jifeng.

228
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:22,840
An inescapable net,

229
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,680
the weak are prey to the strong.

230
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,760
It does not end until death.

231
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,800
Death is life.

232
00:11:30,280 --> 00:11:31,720
Tang Xi, Yuan Ran, and Wu Qiangu,

233
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:32,720
the three of them are acting now.

234
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:42,120
Calculating precisely at every step,

235
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,440
you have calculated me in.

236
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,920
Placing a stone like this,

237
00:11:45,560 --> 00:11:47,760
what a move of creating something from nothing.

238
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,880
The technique is agile and ingenious.

239
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:52,400
If I capture this stone of yours,

240
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,640
you will take the opportunity to shape your formation.

241
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:55,720
However,

242
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:58,000
life is impermanent,

243
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,720
and worldly affairs are unpredictable.

244
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:02,000
Every game having new ideas

245
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,480
is where the chess game's

246
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:06,760
infinite fun lies.

247
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,200
Not contending is best.

248
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,640
While enjoyable,

249
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,800
it cannot compare to

250
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:21,640
the satisfaction of a hearty, slaughtering victory.

251
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,880
Qiao'er, you're still alive.

252
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,080
Father.

253
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,240
You're finally here.

254
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,200
Father.

255
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,200
Do you know?

256
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:42,240
Rumor has it that a Sorcerer's hands...

257
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:45,400
...were imbued with demonic power by ancient gods.

258
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:47,080
Your hands...

259
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,840
...why couldn't they protect me and Mother?

260
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:01,360
Wu Qiangu.

261
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:04,160
The Eastern Depot ordered you to gather secret reports in gambling dens.

262
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,240
Yet you dared to flee with your wife and daughter without permission.

263
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,400
Greed for a single stone...

264
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:17,400
...begets worry and fear.

265
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:21,440
Chess really is like life.

266
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,760
Every step in life...

267
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:23,880
...has its gains and losses.

268
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,000
With every step you take...

269
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:27,680
...you must think carefully...

270
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,680
...before making a decision.

271
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:30,960
Praying to Buddha...

272
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,080
...is not as good as relying on oneself.

273
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:38,800
Husband.

274
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:51,800
I hold the white stones...

275
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,720
...and I have never lost.

276
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:59,920
It is exceptionally quiet today.

277
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:00,760
Indeed.

278
00:15:01,760 --> 00:15:02,400
Without permission...

279
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,440
...trespassing here...

280
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:04,680
...what is your intention?

281
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,080
You really are meddlesome.

282
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,200
The mountain light pleases the birds...

283
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:36,400
...the pool's shadow empties the heart.

284
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:40,120
Decisive and ruthless.

285
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:42,400
You cannot win by killing alone.

286
00:15:42,880 --> 00:15:43,920
Sometimes...

287
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:46,640
...it looks more like the act of a rash youth.

288
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:50,000
Collapsing at the first charge.

289
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:55,760
It is merely sacrificing a stone to shape the board.

290
00:15:56,680 --> 00:16:00,120
Sacrificing stones to shape is just delaying the inevitable.

291
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,440
Your liberties are too tight.

292
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:04,240
It will be hard to end this well, won't it?

293
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:09,240
Showy fists against castles in the air.

294
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,320
Nothing special.

295
00:16:26,160 --> 00:16:27,480
Senior, your strength is passable.

296
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:28,800
Your killing intent is strong enough.

297
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:31,760
But it is a pity your understanding is lacking.

298
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:34,520
Of those who made me kill for real these years...

299
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:35,840
...you are the second.

300
00:16:39,280 --> 00:16:41,800
Tang Xi, Wu Qiangu, and Yuan Ran, the three of them...

301
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:43,920
...risked their lives to investigate the truth of the tower.

302
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:46,520
I only wish to pray in peace today.

303
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:47,800
I do not wish to worry about worldly matters.

304
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,520
I must trouble Advocate Lu...

305
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:51,200
...to visit the secret report collection point.

306
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,200
There is a secret report collection point at Linggu Temple?

307
00:16:53,880 --> 00:16:55,000
So you knew all along...

308
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:56,000
...that the Eastern Depot's intelligence apparatus...

309
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:57,480
...is right inside the Linggu Temple tower.

310
00:16:58,040 --> 00:16:59,960
We have followed Shang Hua since childhood.

311
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:01,560
Naturally, we know a thing or two about the truth.

312
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,960
After all, it was Shang Hua who petitioned His Majesty...

313
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,240
...to build Linggu Temple.

314
00:17:05,320 --> 00:17:06,720
Only, we have never broken into the tower.

315
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:10,000
The taste of Master Konghui's formation is not pleasant.

316
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,280
It is just a pity...

317
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,720
...that a high monk who knows the heavenly secrets...

318
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:17,320
...is trapped by a layman...

319
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,880
...in this place.

320
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:21,400
This place...

321
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,480
...seems to be Master Konghui's retirement sanctuary...

322
00:17:25,120 --> 00:17:25,960
...but in reality...

323
00:17:26,280 --> 00:17:28,280
...it is a place for the Imperial Family's peace of mind.

324
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:30,920
After all...

325
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:34,200
...they cannot tolerate a second Prime Minister in Black.

326
00:17:34,480 --> 00:17:36,080
Then why didn't you tell Tang Xi and the others beforehand?

327
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,320
Lu Shijie, oh Lu Shijie.

328
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:48,560
It has been three years.

329
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:50,440
You haven't improved a bit.

330
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,520
I hired them to enjoy their services.

331
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:55,120
Even if I told them...

332
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:57,480
...that the Eastern Depot's intelligence agency...

333
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,280
...is inside this tower...

334
00:17:59,840 --> 00:18:01,640
...they would still need to do the same things.

335
00:18:02,280 --> 00:18:03,600
What difference would it make?

336
00:18:03,680 --> 00:18:05,480
This is preparatory work before scouting the environment.

337
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:07,520
If an accident happens because the intelligence was wrong...

338
00:18:07,520 --> 00:18:09,760
...if accidents happen even while scouting...

339
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:12,640
...it means they cannot enter the tower at all.

340
00:18:13,560 --> 00:18:14,520
Advocate Lu.

341
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:16,840
Are you going to the collection point or not?

342
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:18,560
Do you not want to get...

343
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:20,160
...more news about the tower for Tang Xi and the others?

344
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:23,000
I am going right now.

345
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:25,640
Where exactly is the secret report collection point?

346
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,480
Even Lu Shijie, too weak to lift a hand,

347
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:44,000
a scholar unable to carry a burden,

348
00:18:44,280 --> 00:18:45,680
has gone to meet the Eastern Depot guards.

349
00:18:46,320 --> 00:18:47,280
Are you satisfied now?

350
00:18:48,480 --> 00:18:50,120
It is his duty.

351
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,840
Since when

352
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:55,640
did you start believing in Buddha?

353
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,880
I do not believe in Buddha.

354
00:18:58,600 --> 00:19:00,440
There are plenty of people offering incense in the temple.

355
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,640
One more makes no difference.

356
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:04,880
One less matters not.

357
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:43,600
When meeting a match in chess, seek the advantage.

358
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,840
While the black and white board is undecided.

359
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:48,480
Know that a single move determines victory or defeat.

360
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:50,840
Let nature take its course for a favorable turn.

361
00:19:51,120 --> 00:19:52,160
Amitabha.

362
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:54,480
Female benefactor, what do you seek?

363
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,280
I seek what lies before my eyes.

364
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,040
This is a medium lot.

365
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:59,320
Neither good nor bad.

366
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,040
Success depends on human effort.

367
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:02,840
The opponent has seen through everything.

368
00:20:03,360 --> 00:20:04,440
Whether it succeeds or not

369
00:20:04,520 --> 00:20:05,520
depends on whom the female benefactor

370
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:06,800
chooses to employ.

371
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:08,680
Amitabha.

372
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:22,920
A deceptive move.

373
00:20:23,040 --> 00:20:24,360
Seemingly full of flaws,

374
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:25,560
yet hiding deep intent.

375
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:27,760
Old fool.

376
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:29,560
Just watch how I strike.

377
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:37,040
I really didn't expect

378
00:20:37,360 --> 00:20:39,880
that you would play such a flamboyant style.

379
00:20:42,640 --> 00:20:43,960
I wouldn't call it a preference.

380
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,040
I am just

381
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:46,560
trying.

382
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:48,280
Just trying.

383
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,320
Do you not feel

384
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:54,920
this is very much like

385
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:56,800
the sorcery of the chess game?

386
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,840
Magnificent and beautiful,

387
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:00,960
yet full of killing intent.

388
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:02,640
Is it?

389
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,480
No.

390
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,080
This is the Ghost Array.

391
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:20,200
Everything before the eyes is void.

392
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:22,600
Illusions easily turn into demons.

393
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,600
Better not to look.

394
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:28,480
The past cannot be helped.

395
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:29,840
We

396
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:32,000
have a long future ahead.

397
00:21:38,840 --> 00:21:40,320
The Three Realms are all suffering.

398
00:21:41,200 --> 00:21:43,000
Buddha delivers all living beings.

399
00:21:43,400 --> 00:21:44,560
I shall deliver you.

400
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:57,960
Yuan Ran.

401
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:00,680
Do not fall into obsession.

402
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,680
A mere puppet formation.

403
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:12,000
Without a heart, there is no feeling.

404
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,640
The puppet was never my husband.

405
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:15,000
It merely carried my affection.

406
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:15,840
At this moment,

407
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,480
it is finally time to make an end of it.

408
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:35,880
The fortune of the game

409
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,640
has shown a clear sign.

410
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:40,160
Abandoned piece.

411
00:22:41,360 --> 00:22:44,080
You should help your chess pieces.

412
00:22:44,600 --> 00:22:47,040
They are all risking their lives for you.

413
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:49,360
Thanks to your guidance.

414
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,360
A winning game

415
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:52,960
naturally brings joy.

416
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,480
If it is a losing game,

417
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:56,400
one enjoys the endless fun of it.

418
00:22:57,680 --> 00:22:58,760
It is just a game of chess.

419
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:00,000
I do not contend.

420
00:23:00,840 --> 00:23:02,160
Borrowing your sentiment.

421
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:03,920
Chess is like life.

422
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:06,400
Fame and fortune rise and fall.

423
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:07,920
If you lose,

424
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:12,960
you don't always get a chance to restart the game.

425
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,200
It is about time.

426
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,040
Let's go.

427
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:43,080
Zhang Shaoqing

428
00:23:43,600 --> 00:23:44,560
Where is the cat I entrusted to you?

429
00:23:45,120 --> 00:23:45,640
That...

430
00:23:45,800 --> 00:23:46,400
It's here.

431
00:23:49,280 --> 00:23:50,160
Zhang Shaoqing.

432
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:52,720
Can't wait to offer incense and ask for a fortune stick?

433
00:23:54,120 --> 00:23:54,880
Where is Legal Advocate Lu?

434
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:56,280
He went to deliver something for me.

435
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,720
He should be back very soon.

436
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,480
Then permit me to inquire out of curiosity.

437
00:24:00,440 --> 00:24:01,960
Legal Advocate Lu is at Linggu Temple.

438
00:24:02,280 --> 00:24:03,680
What is he delivering for Blossom Pavilion?

439
00:24:03,840 --> 00:24:04,600
And where is it going?

440
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:05,760
Zhang Shaoqing.

441
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:06,720
About this...

442
00:24:07,800 --> 00:24:09,400
You should ask the one beside you,

443
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:10,640
Official Shen, instead.

444
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,240
Speak.

445
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,200
There's nothing left to hide, is there?

446
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:17,880
The Blossom Pavilion sleeper agents...

447
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:20,200
The secret dossiers collected for the Eastern Depot...

448
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:21,960
Are all to be sent to Linggu Temple.

449
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:23,360
Lu Shijie...

450
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,040
Must have gone to deliver the secret reports.

451
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:41,480
Look at this murderous posture.

452
00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:44,000
This can't possibly be a friendly spar.

453
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,960
The person fighting Tang Xi...

454
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,680
Seems to be Director Shang's personal guard, Jifeng.

455
00:24:50,040 --> 00:24:50,880
The two are fighting...

456
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:53,080
Tang Xi must have threatened my adoptive father's safety.

457
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:53,640
Hold on.

458
00:24:55,080 --> 00:24:56,840
This person is the world's number one swordsman, Jifeng.

459
00:24:57,080 --> 00:24:59,480
It is indeed Jifeng, who comes from the same sect as Tang Xi.

460
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,240
Reasonably speaking,

461
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,400
Tang Xi should call him "Uncle".

462
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,960
It should be "murderer of his father," right?

463
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:09,040
Jifeng was born to the old master of the Tang Clan...

464
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:10,760
And a maid with no status.

465
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:12,800
Since it is a private vendetta and family scandal,

466
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:15,720
It is inconvenient for us outsiders to interfere.

467
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,720
If you want to go forward and arrest them,

468
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:18,640
There is nothing improper about it.

469
00:25:22,120 --> 00:25:22,960
Arresting them now...

470
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,640
Would easily arouse others' speculation.

471
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:27,080
Better to observe the situation first before acting.

472
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:28,440
Indeed.

473
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:30,560
If Tang Xi is killed,

474
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:32,160
There will be no witness to testify,

475
00:25:32,280 --> 00:25:34,200
And the case of Li Chenyang's abduction can be closed.

476
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,480
Everyone will be happy.

477
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:37,000
According to Lady Hua,

478
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:39,080
Should we be hoping that Tang Xi...

479
00:25:39,120 --> 00:25:40,400
Is killed by Jifeng?

480
00:25:40,760 --> 00:25:41,840
Is this not...

481
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,960
A setup by the Grand Court of Justice and the Eastern Depot...

482
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:46,120
To have them killed under other charges?

483
00:25:46,400 --> 00:25:48,120
Director Wang, please do not speculate vainly.

484
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:49,160
Our methods of solving cases...

485
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:59,000
You aren't thinking of running, are you?

486
00:25:59,000 --> 00:25:59,600
Run?

487
00:26:00,760 --> 00:26:01,520
I, Tang Xi...

488
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:03,600
Known in the Jianghu as Gateless.

489
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:04,880
Hell has no gate.

490
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:05,880
Furthermore,

491
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:08,040
I cannot live under the same sky as my father's killer.

492
00:26:09,080 --> 00:26:10,160
Your life belongs to me.

493
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,320
Truly...

494
00:26:11,320 --> 00:26:13,240
An arrogant brat raised by the Tang Clan.

495
00:26:14,080 --> 00:26:16,280
I remember your father once sought Master Konghui...

496
00:26:16,560 --> 00:26:17,440
To tell your fortune.

497
00:26:17,840 --> 00:26:19,440
Sword pointed at the laughing heavens,

498
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:21,560
Heaven pities the hero's talent.

499
00:26:22,600 --> 00:26:24,120
Joy comes from within sorrow,

500
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,440
The soul seeks to break in dreams.

501
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:26,720
It sounds both arrogant...

502
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:27,640
And short-lived.

503
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:46,560
This round...

504
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,080
I have won.

505
00:26:58,800 --> 00:26:59,720
He has stopped breathing.

506
00:27:03,560 --> 00:27:06,080
Killed by the Tang Clan young master, Tang Xi.

507
00:27:11,560 --> 00:27:12,240
However, the Grand Court of Justice

508
00:27:12,280 --> 00:27:13,680
does have records of major crimes committed by Jifeng.

509
00:27:14,320 --> 00:27:16,360
Wanted for years but never brought to justice.

510
00:27:17,120 --> 00:27:18,320
I wonder how the Embroidered Uniform Guard officer

511
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:19,440
intends to handle this.

512
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:22,400
Tang Xi won the duel against Jifeng with his swordsmanship.

513
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:24,280
His future will be anything but simple.

514
00:27:25,640 --> 00:27:26,680
If he cannot be used by us,

515
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:27,920
he may become a great threat.

516
00:27:29,440 --> 00:27:30,640
If he takes his place,

517
00:27:32,240 --> 00:27:33,760
since the Grand Court of Justice has a warrant,

518
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,720
then let the Grand Court of Justice

519
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,320
decide on Jifeng's old cases.

520
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:38,720
Thank you, Lord Shen.

521
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,800
Later, I will have Shuimo and the others

522
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:42,200
take the body back to the Grand Court of Justice.

523
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,560
Congratulations, Young Master Tang.

524
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:46,920
You go out to offer incense,

525
00:27:47,360 --> 00:27:49,480
and manage to catch a heinous criminal.

526
00:27:50,160 --> 00:27:50,920
However, in a while,

527
00:27:51,040 --> 00:27:52,560
you must come with me to the Grand Court of Justice to give a statement.

528
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:54,000
The pupil...

529
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,440
...surpasses the master.

530
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,280
A great sword does not clash,

531
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:59,040
yet life and death are inches away.

532
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:02,080
Young Master Tang's martial prowess and talent...

533
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:03,840
...I admire greatly.

534
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:06,040
If you are willing to replace Jifeng,

535
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:08,040
in the future, the entire Tang Clan

536
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:09,880
will be under the protection of my Eastern Depot.

537
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:12,200
No thanks.

538
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:14,320
I don't have that strong a sense of responsibility.

539
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:16,560
Besides, a position in the Depots or Guard

540
00:28:16,560 --> 00:28:17,800
is both hateful and dangerous.

541
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:19,560
It doesn't suit me.

542
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:23,040
Tang Xi.

543
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:24,600
Such an opportunity...

544
00:28:25,280 --> 00:28:26,600
...is not something everyone gets.

545
00:28:26,760 --> 00:28:28,560
Jifeng served Director Shang

546
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:31,080
for over ten years.

547
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:32,960
His bones are not yet cold,

548
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,240
and you are in such a rush to recruit me.

549
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:37,320
What do you think I feel about that?

550
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:40,080
You all laugh at me for being mad,

551
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,560
but I think you are the crazy ones.

552
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:46,680
Young man.

553
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,640
You are very dangerous.

554
00:28:50,080 --> 00:28:50,680
Youzhi.

555
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,360
I was playing chess with the Master

556
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:53,760
and it drained my spirit.

557
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,560
Escort me to the wing room to rest.

558
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:56,640
Yes.

559
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:11,400
You little lunatic.

560
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:12,560
Look out for yourself.

561
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:21,760
Master.

562
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:24,160
Why are you interested now

563
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:26,600
in playing such a taxing game?

564
00:29:28,840 --> 00:29:30,680
I suddenly felt an interest today

565
00:29:31,280 --> 00:29:33,600
to tease that old castrated thief.

566
00:29:34,080 --> 00:29:34,760
How about this?

567
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,560
I will play a game with you.

568
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,000
Master, you go first.

569
00:29:42,520 --> 00:29:43,080
I'll let you have the advantage.

570
00:29:43,520 --> 00:29:43,880
Good.

571
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:56,600
Director Shang.

572
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:58,440
Why have you returned?

573
00:29:59,200 --> 00:29:59,920
Master.

574
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:02,600
I can distinguish the footsteps of ordinary people.

575
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:13,040
Zhang Yi has returned.

576
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:17,040
I won.

577
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:18,760
Your eyes are playing tricks on you.

578
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:19,360
Master.

579
00:30:20,080 --> 00:30:21,120
My eyesight is perfectly fine.

580
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:22,520
Don't try to cheat now.

581
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:30,520
I made a wrong move.

582
00:30:30,840 --> 00:30:31,680
I should have moved here.

583
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:32,880
Then...

584
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:36,040
...I win.

585
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:42,480
I lost.

586
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:45,440
It is rare for us to gather here,

587
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:47,080
but we should not stay long.

588
00:30:48,080 --> 00:30:49,200
It has become rather uninteresting.

589
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:01,400
The moment of Zen has arrived.

590
00:31:03,080 --> 00:31:05,240
Sentient beings are limitless,

591
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:11,760
amidst the light of the water and moon.

592
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:44,760
Dream of Divine Secrets

593
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:47,400
Your dream

594
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:48,800
and my dream,

595
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:50,240
how are they different?

596
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:51,920
Youzhi.

597
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:53,840
Father.

598
00:31:54,080 --> 00:31:56,320
Leave the Embroidered Uniform Guards you brought

599
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,560
to protect Master Konghui's body.

600
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,600
All the monks in the temple

601
00:32:01,080 --> 00:32:02,120
must use the highest etiquette

602
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:04,320
to care for the Master's remains.

603
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:06,760
There must be no mistakes.

604
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:07,800
Rest assured, Father.

605
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:09,680
Master Konghui's passing

606
00:32:10,320 --> 00:32:11,080
is a matter of great importance

607
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,440
concerning the dignity of the state.

608
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,560
I have arranged everything properly.

609
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,240
You may enter the palace

610
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:18,080
to report to His Majesty.

611
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:36,080
Young Master Tang,

612
00:32:36,600 --> 00:32:38,640
you've impressed me again today.

613
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,040
The terrain around Linggu Temple's tower

614
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:42,560
and the methods to enter it

615
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:43,400
have been clearly investigated.

616
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:45,400
But there is only one chance.

617
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:47,400
Today, Master Konghui passed away.

618
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:49,560
Tonight is the best time to act.

619
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:51,920
Since Young Master Tang has a plan,

620
00:32:52,520 --> 00:32:54,200
then go ahead and act freely.

621
00:32:54,840 --> 00:32:55,760
As for the rest,

622
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:57,600
just as we agreed,

623
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,160
I will no longer interfere.

624
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:07,440
Zhang Shaoqing,

625
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,040
what are you thinking about?

626
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,760
I am thinking about Tang Xi.

627
00:33:15,840 --> 00:33:16,520
Zhang Shaoqing,

628
00:33:17,040 --> 00:33:18,480
your thoughts are dangerous right now.

629
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,240
Have you ever heard

630
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:22,280
that a decent woman kidnapped by bandits,

631
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:24,600
especially after receiving small favors,

632
00:33:25,360 --> 00:33:27,080
might start to like them?

633
00:33:27,520 --> 00:33:28,480
I was thinking,

634
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:31,080
what are they really doing at Linggu Temple?

635
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:32,320
Why risk their lives

636
00:33:32,320 --> 00:33:33,760
to enter Linggu Temple from elsewhere?

637
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:36,320
The high tower.

638
00:33:39,200 --> 00:33:39,680
I think

639
00:33:41,080 --> 00:33:43,520
they are scouting the central tower's environment.

640
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:46,120
Did they risk their lives entering the tower

641
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,760
just to steal the relics of past high monks?

642
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,320
Besides the relics of past high monks,

643
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,880
the high tower's main function

644
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:56,360
is to store the Eastern Depot's secret reports

645
00:33:56,360 --> 00:33:57,720
and house the main mechanisms.

646
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:01,800
So...

647
00:34:03,280 --> 00:34:04,320
So Director Wang

648
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:06,000
is assisting them in scouting the environment.

649
00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:08,520
It coincides with Master Konghui's passing today.

650
00:34:10,200 --> 00:34:11,120
There is no day

651
00:34:11,120 --> 00:34:12,120
more suitable than today to break into the tower

652
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:13,560
and expose the Eastern Depot's secrets.

653
00:34:26,680 --> 00:34:28,920
Vice Commander Yin Feng greets the Director-in-chief.

654
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:29,400
Speak.

655
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:31,120
My Lord,

656
00:34:32,640 --> 00:34:33,760
according to our investigation,

657
00:34:34,080 --> 00:34:35,480
members of the Four Directions were at Linggu Temple today

658
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,200
conducting secret reconnaissance.

659
00:34:36,600 --> 00:34:37,880
The illusionists and killers in the bamboo forest

660
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:39,000
have all been killed.

661
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,160
The swamp puppet array was also destroyed.

662
00:34:41,520 --> 00:34:43,120
Now that Master Konghui has passed away,

663
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,360
I believe

664
00:34:45,240 --> 00:34:46,200
they are definitely targeting

665
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:47,440
the high tower of Linggu Temple.

666
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,640
The Linggu Temple high tower

667
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,680
has an impregnable defensive structure.

668
00:34:52,200 --> 00:34:54,320
No accidents have occurred in ten years.

669
00:34:55,720 --> 00:34:56,880
But it is better to be prepared.

670
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:01,200
Vice Commander Yin Feng, hear my order.

671
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:01,480
Vice Commander Yin Feng, hear my order.

672
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:02,640
Your subordinate is here.

673
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,320
You will personally lead

674
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:05,960
Embroidered Uniform Guard Warden Shen Youzhi,

675
00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:07,640
Battalion Commander Yuan Ling,

676
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:08,920
Zhang Yi of the Grand Court of Justice,

677
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,400
and one hundred Embroidered Uniform Guards

678
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:12,000
to go guard Linggu Temple.

679
00:35:12,160 --> 00:35:13,000
Do not fail.

680
00:35:13,280 --> 00:35:13,960
As you command.
